],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The word “money” is substituted for “dollars” for consistency in the revised title. The words “the International Monetary Fund” are omitted as obsolete because of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1976-10-19/s9"},"text":"section 9 of the Act of October 19, 1976","children":[],"tail":" ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/564"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–564","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/2661"},"text":"90 Stat. 2661","children":[],"tail":")."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
